room_title: Escape room "Back Alley" by The Escape Room in Winston-Salem
room_address: 3191 Peters Creek Parkway Winston Salem, NC 27127
room_description: Walking home from a night out with your friends, you all are captured and locked in a back alley by a street gang. Before any harm is done, they decide to give you a chance to escape your doom. You and your friends have one hour to successfully play the gang's games to escape, or risk never having another night out again!
